<div
class="entry-content">
<p>You can email us at support@bridecity.com to cancel your order. Order can be canceled only if the item is not shipped by the seller.
 <strong>Unfortunately, an order cannot be cancelled in case an order has already been sent to customer.</strong>
 </p><ul>
 <br>
<br>
 <li>If your order has not been shipped and you have paid the amount via debit card/credit card/Netbanking, the complete amount including shipping charges will be refunded to the same account from which the payment was made.</li>
 <br>
<br>
 <li>In case the order has been shipped, no refunds will be provided in case of payment via debit card/ credit card / Netbanking. If the order is not accepted at the time of delivery, the amount will be provided in form of store credits to the customer in their account that can be used in any further purchases at any point of time.</li>
 
 <br>
<br>
<li>In case of payment via cash on delivery, if the order is not accepted, cash on delivery will not be allowed in any future purchases for the customer.</li></ul></div></div></main></div></div></div>
